1. *Vidim* da si se promenio. (I see that you have changed.)
2. On je rekao da me *vidi* u petak. (He said that he will see me on Friday.)
3. Posetio sam tvoju kuću, ali te nisam *vidim*. (I visited your house, but I didn't see you.)
4. *Videvši* njegove izjave, rešio sam da se ne mešam. (Seeing his statements, I decided not to interfere.)
5. Ona je *videla* tvoju poruku. (She saw your message.)